        <p>What's the point of a collaboration system if you can't bring everyone aboard? activeCollab&reg; lets you include all the people you want to work with on any number of projects. activeCollab&reg; sets up on your own web server</p>
        <p>Your team will have a place where they can work together, discuss projects and tasks, exchange files and more. Additionally, you can include clients, contractors, suppliers and everybody else you are working with, while having full control over who can see and do what.</p>
