      	<h1>Manage Projects</h1>
        <p>activeCollab&reg; is all about projects and getting them done. You can create as many projects as you want and invite people to work on them.</p>
        <p>Project work is organized around important project milestones, where each milestone can have its own set of tasks, dicussions and files. When your team finishes work on one milestone, they move to the next one until the whole project is done.</p>
