      	<h1>Share Files</h1>
        <p>Working on a project usually means sharing a lot of files. activeCollab&reg; gives people the tools to share, organize and comment on them.</p>
        <p>Files are organized into categories and sorted by the time they are uploaded. The system is able to track different versions of a file so you can see how it has evolved.</p>
        <p>When you upload an image, activeCollab&reg; will generate a thumbnail for quick preview.</p>
