      	<h1>Email Integration</h1>
        <p>activeCollab&reg; keeps you and your associates in the loop by sending email notifications about new tickets, comments, file versions and more.</p>
        <p>activeCollab&reg; lets you reply to all notifications sent to you via email. When your reply is received, it is submitted as a comment in the same thread.</p>
        <p>When the system receives a message that is not a reply, it creates a new ticket or discussion based on it.</p>
