      <div class="tour_item_top_block_content">
      	<h1>Keep Control</h1>
        <p>While most project management and collaboration tools on the market today are controlled by their vendors, it's great to be able to host a system on your server and have full control over it.</p>
        <p>activeCollab&reg; has powerful and flexible role and permission systems that let you configure who has access to Tickets, Documents, Files, Discussions, etc.</p>
        <p>All your data is safe from prying eyes and you always have full control over it.</p>
      </div>
